 BUCO Nelspruit this week made a massive donation of R400 000 worth of building materials to Nelspruit Primary School. This will allow the school to landscape outdoor play areas, sporting grounds, repurpose the pavilion, and maintain the tennis and netball courts. ALSO READ: Another 157 Santa Shoeboxes needed to help less fortunate As a way to give back to the community which supports them, BUCO is making a significant impact on the school.    The school will be able to complete the renovations on the outdoor area, classrooms and cafeteria and start to prepare for the hosting of the interprimary athletics in 2022. ALSO READ: Donate a tree and feed the needy BUCO NELSPRUIT will stay in partnership with Nelspruit Primary and keep on “building” them and the community.